    "body": "Thanks for raising this, this is indeed a bug due to improper toml for the `optimizer_details` table.\r\nfixed in https://github.com/gakonst/foundry/pull/795\r\n\r\nto make this work, you'd need to change it to\r\n\r\n```toml\r\n[default.optimizer_details]\r\nyul = false\r\n```\r\n ",
